platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: From recruiting incoming freshmen to tracking player GPAs, this clever collegiate spin on Retro Bowl turns you into the big manager on campus.
From recruiting freshers to tracking player GPAs, this clever spin on Retro Bowl turns you into the big manager on campus.
在這款《Retro Bowl》的衍生遊戲中，化身校園球隊總經理，從招募新生到追蹤球員 GPA，均由你一手包辦。
